ai-patthana23.3:0.2_0: under the investigation of principles means to the extent of the Dhamma.
ai-patthana23.3:1.1_0: Not is skilled in the Teaching, not for the sake of good will, for the sake of non-violence, and for the objection of the teaching.
ai-patthana23.3:1.1_2: There is in brief, three drops near the middle sections on the ground, and five or three.
ai-patthana23.3:1.1_3: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana23.3:2.1_0: Not for the sake of profitableness, or for the sake of grasping?
ai-patthana23.3:2.1_3: the five hindrances are not clear.
ai-patthana23.3:3.1_0: Not grasping arises in someone who isn’t skillful because of not grasping. Grasping goodness arises dependent on the skillful, causes and reasons.
